    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4–15</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>While NON- doesn't score heavily on its own, the tiles are extremely common — N appears 6 times and O appears 8 times in the bag. You'll frequently hold N-O-N without trying, making this prefix a reliable extension option.</p>

