    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Dump duplicate N tiles:</span> With 6 N tiles in the bag, you often get stuck with two. NON- is the perfect way to use both N tiles productively while setting up a longer word.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
